

1. Cannot run on latest browsers versions. Can be updated to Selenium 3 and latest versions of Serenity
2. CSS selectors can be shortened ex: when class has 2 or 3 words we can just use only for selector
3. Page wait methods and Element presents methods to be implemented to avoid test flakiness
4. Rerun failed tests can be implemented
5. Aggregate reports can be implemented
6. Can be extended to mobile responsive tests with different screen sizes

